
gdb --args executablename arg1 arg2 arg3
(gdb) set output-radix 16
(gdb) x/5i 0x001004013D2
(gdb) break *0x0000000000400448
backtrace full

Obtain function names and number lines from a core and a executable: addr2line
addr2line -e ./c2m-pma.exe 0x0000000100420129

